<span id="freeTextContainer6445228222250628213"><strong>Not what I was expecting</strong><br/><br/>This book far exceeded my expectations. There were times I gasped and teared up as the story progressed and we find out the truth. My heart broke as we delved more into this story. Very well written and very emotiona. Glad I read it.</span>

